# BeVinci source hygiene policy.
#
# This file defines the desired future policy. Existing files are not normalized
# in this commit. Any line-ending normalization must happen in a separate,
# explicit hygiene commit.

* text=auto

*.cpp text
*.h text
*.hpp text
*.c text
*.cc text
*.md text eol=lf
*.json text eol=lf
*.txt text eol=lf

*.png binary
*.jpg binary
*.jpeg binary
*.odt binary
*.pdf binary
*.ico binary
